videos.description: Jalen Smith slips past the Purdue defense and rises for an easy two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Smith throws down powerful slam

videos.description: Darryl Morsell shows off his bounce as he gets up for a monster slam.
videos.headline: Morsell skies for vicious slam

videos.description: Purdue turns good defense into easy offense as Carsen Edwards comes up with a steal and follows up with a tomahawk slam.
videos.headline: Edwards punishes the rim on tomahawk slam

videos.description: Maryland's Anthony Cowan lobs it up to Jalen Smith who throws down the emphatic alley-oop jam.
videos.headline: Smith slams home alley-oop
